divs: Sighting Details I was standing on my deck when I looked up at thestars and saw a figure 8 with lights pass over at great speed..faster than a jetbut slower than a falling star...so I assumed id seen a ufo...second time in mylife...please let me know if this has been observed by anyone else. by theway..there was no sound...no sound at all.
